<item>
            <title>[LU-13121] ll_update_lsm_md() may deadlock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13121</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ll_update_lsm_md() down_write() if lli-&amp;gt;lli_lsm_md is NULL, and tries to initialize it, but if a concurrent lookup initialized lli-&amp;gt;lli_lsm_md after this check and before taking write lock, it will up_read(), so the write lock is not released, therefore subsequent lookup will deadlock on this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="57770">LU-13121</key>
            <summary>ll_update_lsm_md() may deadlock</summary>
